rovides a number of investment opportunities within the senior housing industry but its latest offering senior living fund i is the first fund that is diversified across several new senior housing development projects across the usa now senior living fund principal dan brewer says the firm projects that it will exhaust the investment units that offer the highest rate of return sometime between the end of february through early march he strongly encourages interested investors to contact the company by the end of february to reserve these units as the baby boomer generation ages the number of americans ages  and older is estimated to increase by about  million to reach a total population of  million currently approximately  new senior housing units are added annually to keep up with this explosive growth in seniors the country will require up to  new units per year an increase of  over current development levels for this reason brewer says investing in senior housing is a prudent longterm investment strategy we focus exclusively on housing operators with a strong history and track record of success we believe the strength of the operator is the number one indicator of the viability of a senior housing project not only have we developed relationships with many senior housing operators but with other key resources within the senior housing industry as well says brewer senior living fund i offers four classes of investment tiers class b and d pay the highest preferred rates of return and brewer says they are by far the most popular choice among early investors interested parties need to contact the firm during february and the company will work with investors to complete their investment senior living fund i is only available to accredited investors approximately onethird of investors use an ira about senior living fund llc senior living fund is an investment opportunity for americans who would like to have a hand in helping to provide housing to aging us seniors as the